{"tid":950810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"達文西機械臂事故 美十年收兩萬投訴","createTime":"2018-12-21T21:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T02:28:43.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f0280ec85d3f600505eae93d14e587976eed36aa","tid":950810,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T21:25:33.000Z","msg":"【大公報訊】據美國NBC報道：美國直覺外科手術公司研發的「達文西機械臂」能提高手術精準度，已在全球許多醫院使用。不過，美國全國廣播公司（NBC）20日報道稱，美國食品和藥物管理局（FDA）在過去十年中，共收到來自病患及醫生的超過20000份針對達文西手術機械臂的投訴。<br />\n　　<br />\n在投訴中，超過2000名病人受傷，274人死亡，並有17000宗手術出現機器故障，如機械臂失靈或隔熱層裂開掉入病患體內等。其中，艾奧瓦州女子費瑟斯通2015年在醫生推薦下使用達文西機械臂進行子宮切除手術，但術後出現輸尿管灼傷、腎積水及結腸受損等，醫生證實是機械臂造成。<br />\n　　<br />\nNBC還發現，在FDA接到的投訴中，有不少將多個案例寫在同一份報告中，甚至有一份報告包含200個受傷案例。因此，實際受傷人數可能達到4000人。<br />\n　　<br />\n另外，據FDA數據，機器在過去十年中被召回175次，2014年最多為49次，2010和2011年均降為1次，而2018年有8次。<br />\n　　<br />\n達文西機械臂自2000年上市以來廣泛普及。NBC報道稱，美國在2013至2017年間利用達文西機械臂進行的手術數量增加了52%，在2017年達到70萬宗機械臂手術，因此出現問題的比例不算高。<br />\n　　<br />\n另外，香港醫管局下轄的5間公立醫院也設有「達文西機械臂」手術系統，每年約進行1000宗手術，但目前未有此類事故報告發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232111/2018/1222/223629.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fnews%2F232111%2F2018%2F1222%2F223629.html&d=v5ULw9joTTlZplBFgqv%2BGRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4637a58b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232111/2018/1222/223629.html</a>"},{"pid":"fe130a2cc2b3cda69676794e0baf067da7b38e04","tid":950810,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T21:28:02.000Z","msg":"達聞西"},{"pid":"8149ce62142ca1f9a8be2252d7674f07b15b615e","tid":950810,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T22:08:09.000Z","msg":"QMH都有一部"},{"pid":"1d02fbc0502bc6f6146e23815658fdef2c20bb14","tid":950810,"uid":195570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T22:10:34.000Z","msg":"機械會損耗，check 清楚係監管者責任"},{"pid":"bfa3bb40265f37156097222bb50be82030765d44","tid":950810,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T22:27:15.000Z","msg":"同人手比較呢"},{"pid":"42cc25fa2d1e4de1cee0f38d59fb9f91f091f0df","tid":950810,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d02fbc0502bc6f6146e23815658fdef2c20bb14","tid":950810,"uid":195570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T22:10:34.000Z","msg":"機械會損耗，check 清楚係監管者責任"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T23:18:12.000Z","msg":"其實da vinci 本身間廠training 俾唔足前線醫生<br />\n<br />\n利申:做緊相關行業嘅開發"},{"pid":"6af7c8924c804556bd7ce64077929e826e62c179","tid":950810,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T00:12:57.000Z","msg":"妓者<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2014年最多為49次，2010和2011年均降為1次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係2010同2011 都僅為一次，至2014 激增至高峰49次，其後回落"},{"pid":"24b594a71f890d474c383ed49fd7ded2119d8075","tid":950810,"uid":61882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://guides.gamepressure.com/hitman/gfx/word/520772958.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fguides.gamepressure.com%2Fhitman%2Fgfx%2Fword%2F520772958.jpg&h=3ba4ebfd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d45e42f5471766797a035fafde8e3d8fc7d5ab1","tid":950810,"uid":151496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:13:53.000Z","msg":"其實無人講過全美十年來透過達文西總共做過幾多單手術<br />\n<br />\n分分鐘過億宗失得兩萬宗，香港醫療事故仲多"},{"pid":"82fab667006c669e512501b25fb9121b2efdeee6","tid":950810,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:20:56.000Z","msg":"睇頭三個字已經可以上一頁"},{"pid":"e9c2d31f31390f129398c890f59e42febbdc1927","tid":950810,"uid":103936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"個專利就完 開始唱衰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}